1
00:00:17,809 --> 00:00:19,430
Where's your gambler father hiding?

2
00:00:19,610 --> 00:00:21,549
You want to run away from your debts?

3
00:00:22,969 --> 00:00:25,169
How dare you glare at me?

4
00:00:34,370 --> 00:00:35,629
Full score?

5
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:38,250
This old bastard raised a top student.

6
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:47,570
If you don't tell me where your father is hiding,

7
00:00:47,950 --> 00:00:49,430
I'll disable you.

8
00:00:52,409 --> 00:00:53,089
Stop!

9
00:00:58,329 --> 00:00:58,869
What are you doing?

10
00:01:04,950 --> 00:01:06,769
Beauty, this is none of your business.

11
00:01:06,769 --> 00:01:08,210
How dare you interfere?

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,390
I've called the police.

13
00:01:10,930 --> 00:01:12,129
You can't hurt him anymore.

14
00:01:17,390 --> 00:01:19,469
Today, for the sake of this beauty,

15
00:01:19,469 --> 00:01:21,549
boy, we'll meet again.

16
00:01:22,049 --> 00:01:22,629
Leave.

17
00:01:24,810 --> 00:01:25,730
You just wait.

18
00:01:31,230 --> 00:01:33,510
Fortunately, I scared them away.

19
00:01:34,610 --> 00:01:37,170
I'll call an ambulance for you.

20
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:49,909
Here.

21
00:02:08,510 --> 00:02:11,349
♪I want to hold a bunch of sunshine and walk towards you.♪

22
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,870
♪But fate♪

23
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:16,769
♪always makes you see♪

24
00:02:16,769 --> 00:02:19,730
♪the way I struggle in the mud.♪

25
00:02:54,929 --> 00:02:55,549
Please enjoy.

26
00:02:55,549 --> 00:02:56,429
Thank you.

27
00:02:57,989 --> 00:03:00,369
Except for the information released on the trading website,

28
00:03:00,369 --> 00:03:02,209
there are no other clues.

29
00:03:03,410 --> 00:03:05,130
The murderer seems to have completely disappeared.

30
00:03:07,070 --> 00:03:09,890
But I think the murderer knows me very well.

31
00:03:11,049 --> 00:03:12,369
If it was an ordinary kidnapper,

32
00:03:13,049 --> 00:03:14,230
he would have directly used Wu Xi

33
00:03:14,769 --> 00:03:15,809
to ask me for ransom.

34
00:03:16,809 --> 00:03:17,450
The reason why they didn't do that

35
00:03:18,329 --> 00:03:19,450
is that they are certain

36
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:20,730
that after my death,

37
00:03:21,170 --> 00:03:22,690
they can use Wu Xi to get my inheritance,

38
00:03:23,089 --> 00:03:23,950
or even the Chenghai Group.

39
00:03:25,890 --> 00:03:26,809
There are not many people

40
00:03:27,010 --> 00:03:28,649
who know the internal operations

41
00:03:29,329 --> 00:03:29,869
of the Group.

42
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:31,829
There is another possibility.

43
00:03:32,309 --> 00:03:33,589
It's Zhou Xubai.

44
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:37,390
He created this accident

45
00:03:37,890 --> 00:03:40,450
just to get you.

46
00:03:45,510 --> 00:03:46,529
It shouldn't be him.

47
00:03:47,249 --> 00:03:48,890
Is it really not him,

48
00:03:48,890 --> 00:03:50,890
or you just don't want it to be him?

49
00:03:55,529 --> 00:03:57,230
I have nothing to do with him.

50
00:03:58,329 --> 00:04:00,290
There's no need to deceive myself.

51
00:04:02,269 --> 00:04:03,589
They think

52
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,769
I'm a greenhouse flower,

53
00:04:06,410 --> 00:04:07,989
a prey at their mercy.

54
00:04:08,809 --> 00:04:10,470
I won't let them have their way.

55
00:04:11,329 --> 00:04:12,809
Only by standing in the eye of the storm

56
00:04:13,730 --> 00:04:15,329
can we see the source of the whirlpool.

57
00:04:17,110 --> 00:04:17,670
I'm ready

58
00:04:18,610 --> 00:04:19,549
to go back to the company tomorrow

59
00:04:19,549 --> 00:04:20,910
and take back control.

60
00:04:22,529 --> 00:04:23,589
My little rose

61
00:04:23,690 --> 00:04:24,949
finally grew thorns.

62
00:04:26,009 --> 00:04:27,170
I'll support you all the way.

63
00:04:38,689 --> 00:04:39,569
Zhi Mei,

64
00:04:40,189 --> 00:04:41,470
the operation of the group is complex.

65
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:43,509
It's normal that

66
00:04:43,809 --> 00:04:45,049
you can't understand these reports.

67
00:04:46,749 --> 00:04:47,610
We all know

68
00:04:47,869 --> 00:04:49,150
your efforts.

69
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:49,809
That's right.

70
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:51,189
These

71
00:04:51,689 --> 00:04:52,629
can't be learned

72
00:04:52,970 --> 00:04:53,869
in a short time.

73
00:04:55,569 --> 00:04:56,069
Yeah.

74
00:04:56,749 --> 00:04:57,910
With us veterans around,

75
00:04:58,850 --> 00:05:00,809
we'll help you manage the group.

76
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:01,830
Just like

77
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:03,410
when your parents were alive,

78
00:05:03,749 --> 00:05:06,350
you can continue to be a carefree princess.

79
00:05:06,710 --> 00:05:07,369
Yeah.

80
00:05:08,770 --> 00:05:09,129
Uncle Zhao,

81
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:12,489
the Nancheng Real Estate project you're in charge of

82
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:14,249
has been delaying payments for months.

83
00:05:14,809 --> 00:05:16,910
Where exactly did the funds go?

84
00:05:17,449 --> 00:05:18,369
I'm afraid we need to have a good talk

85
00:05:18,949 --> 00:05:19,629
to talk about it.

86
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:21,869
President Jiang,

87
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,189
last year,

88
00:05:23,470 --> 00:05:25,530
the overseas R&D acquisition case you promoted

89
00:05:26,590 --> 00:05:27,809
had a final assessment report

90
00:05:27,809 --> 00:05:29,530
that was 35% above the official price.

91
00:05:30,410 --> 00:05:32,249
Do I need to explain to you

92
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:35,650
who invested in this appraisal agency?

93
00:05:37,929 --> 00:05:38,330
Young Master Ye,

94
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:41,710
since you've investigated so thoroughly,

95
00:05:42,410 --> 00:05:43,090
you should know

96
00:05:43,249 --> 00:05:44,929
the difficulties the group is facing.

97
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,129
The stock price has been falling.

98
00:05:47,770 --> 00:05:49,090
The most practical solution now

99
00:05:49,650 --> 00:05:51,470
is for you to withdraw the funds

100
00:05:51,470 --> 00:05:53,009
from your personal trust fund

101
00:05:53,530 --> 00:05:55,429
to help the group get through the crisis.

102
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:59,429
Right, that's correct.

103
00:05:59,929 --> 00:06:01,470
I won't use the security my parents left me

104
00:06:01,809 --> 00:06:03,009
to cover the group's losses.

105
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:05,189
If

106
00:06:06,249 --> 00:06:07,869
this is your plan for me,

107
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:10,030
I think the senior management of Chenghai Group

108
00:06:10,309 --> 00:06:11,530
really needs a major overhaul.

109
00:06:12,569 --> 00:06:13,830
But this isn't a trivial matter.

110
00:06:14,009 --> 00:06:14,670
Indeed.

111
00:06:15,049 --> 00:06:16,530
There's a solid opportunity now.

112
00:06:17,129 --> 00:06:19,150
A powerful multinational corporation

113
00:06:19,330 --> 00:06:20,150
is willing to invest.

114
00:06:20,970 --> 00:06:21,910
If we can partner up,

115
00:06:22,030 --> 00:06:22,770
we might just

116
00:06:22,970 --> 00:06:24,549
save the company.

117
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:29,590
Mr. Ye, what do we do?

118
00:06:29,710 --> 00:06:30,809
Lanze Capital is known

119
00:06:30,809 --> 00:06:31,970
for being tough to deal with.

120
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:34,150
Long time no see,

121
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:47,489
Mr. Ye,

122
00:06:51,489 --> 00:06:53,429
I'm Zhou Xubai, the representative of Lanze.

123
00:06:54,489 --> 00:06:55,549
Nice to meet you again.

124
00:07:08,290 --> 00:07:09,330
According to our due diligence,

125
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:11,670
Chenghai Group's actual debt

126
00:07:11,749 --> 00:07:12,650
and contingent liabilities

127
00:07:12,869 --> 00:07:14,809
far exceed your disclosed data.

128
00:07:15,049 --> 00:07:15,949
The hidden gap

129
00:07:16,030 --> 00:07:17,869
is estimated to be over 1.5 billion.

130
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:21,230
[He knows the situation so well.]

131
00:07:22,869 --> 00:07:24,590
Lanze's investment is not charity.

132
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:28,530
We must ensure the safety of our funds

133
00:07:28,949 --> 00:07:30,369
and get a reasonable return.

134
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:31,749
Therefore,

135
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:33,650
we require a reorganization of the board of directors.

136
00:07:34,249 --> 00:07:36,110
We must have more than half of the seats

137
00:07:36,650 --> 00:07:37,949
and appoint the chief financial officer

138
00:07:38,249 --> 00:07:39,830
to take full charge of the finance

139
00:07:40,170 --> 00:07:40,670
and operation.

140
00:07:42,410 --> 00:07:43,069
Mr. Zhou,

141
00:07:43,650 --> 00:07:44,809
what we need

142
00:07:44,929 --> 00:07:46,369
is a strategic partner,

143
00:07:46,929 --> 00:07:48,509
not a master who takes over everything.

144
00:07:48,989 --> 00:07:50,629
Your requirements are too harsh.

145
00:07:50,970 --> 00:07:51,830
to accept.

146
00:07:55,989 --> 00:07:57,210
Then let's talk about

147
00:07:57,629 --> 00:07:59,509
something you can accept.

148
00:08:01,929 --> 00:08:03,770
I require that during our partnership,

149
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,470
and until the funds are safely withdrawn,

150
00:08:06,330 --> 00:08:07,889
you must remain single

151
00:08:08,410 --> 00:08:09,210
and not get married.

152
00:08:09,489 --> 00:08:09,749
You...

153
00:08:12,290 --> 00:08:13,369
However, as far as I know,

154
00:08:13,730 --> 00:08:14,929
you have been single

155
00:08:15,449 --> 00:08:16,629
since your husband's passing.

156
00:08:17,090 --> 00:08:17,590
That's good.

157
00:08:18,309 --> 00:08:18,970
Keep it up.

158
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:23,970
Mr. Zhou,

159
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:26,530
this is a personal question,

160
00:08:27,249 --> 00:08:28,590
and has nothing to do with business.

161
00:08:29,129 --> 00:08:30,369
You have no right

162
00:08:30,369 --> 00:08:32,110
to make such an unreasonable request.

163
00:08:33,210 --> 00:08:33,770
Nothing to do with business?

164
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:38,590
I'm doing this to ensure the stability of the company's equity,

165
00:08:39,369 --> 00:08:40,810
to avoid the loss of equity

166
00:08:40,889 --> 00:08:42,029
due to marriage,

167
00:08:42,409 --> 00:08:43,389
or unexpected situations.

168
00:08:44,029 --> 00:08:46,409
You should understand this, shouldn't you?

169
00:08:49,610 --> 00:08:51,009
This is a necessary condition for investment.

170
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:53,190
If you refuse,

171
00:08:54,090 --> 00:08:56,210
Lanze will withdraw its investment intention.

172
00:08:56,769 --> 00:08:57,869
Chenghai's future

173
00:08:58,450 --> 00:09:00,369
will be up to you.

174
00:09:28,230 --> 00:09:29,489
What else do you want?

175
00:09:29,789 --> 00:09:31,850
Wasn't the humiliation enough?

176
00:09:32,129 --> 00:09:33,009
Humiliation?

177
00:09:33,649 --> 00:09:35,909
I think that was the fairest condition.

178
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:38,310
You'll do anything to achieve your goals.

179
00:09:39,029 --> 00:09:41,210
You really are disappointing.

180
00:09:44,830 --> 00:09:45,950
So, tell me,

181
00:09:46,230 --> 00:09:47,989
what exactly is my purpose?

182
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:54,590
That's right.

183
00:09:54,889 --> 00:09:57,149
It's the answer you're thinking of.

184
00:09:57,369 --> 00:10:00,310
I've only ever had one goal.

185
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:05,710
I'm afraid

186
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:07,190
you'll be disappointed.

187
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:28,509
Be careful.

188
00:10:29,029 --> 00:10:30,269
I can walk a bit on my own now.

189
00:10:34,690 --> 00:10:35,409
The doctor was right.

190
00:10:37,330 --> 00:10:38,950
Rehabilitation in nature

191
00:10:40,129 --> 00:10:41,129
is indeed more effective.

192
00:10:44,529 --> 00:10:45,210
Zhi Mei,

193
00:10:45,889 --> 00:10:47,070
When my leg gets better,

194
00:10:47,810 --> 00:10:49,190
we'll get remarried

195
00:10:49,970 --> 00:10:50,830
and have another wedding.

196
00:10:55,629 --> 00:10:58,190
The company is not doing well right now,

197
00:10:58,570 --> 00:11:00,009
and there are some things that need to be sorted out.

198
00:11:01,509 --> 00:11:03,230
And the real culprit of the accident hasn't been found yet.

199
00:11:04,190 --> 00:11:04,989
So,

200
00:11:05,389 --> 00:11:05,989
I'm worried.

201
00:11:05,989 --> 00:11:06,430
Yes,

202
00:11:06,649 --> 00:11:07,409
I was too hasty.

203
00:11:07,769 --> 00:11:08,470
It's just a piece of paper,

204
00:11:09,509 --> 00:11:11,050
it can't affect our relationship.

205
00:11:24,029 --> 00:11:25,509
The place beside you

206
00:11:26,009 --> 00:11:26,889
has always been

207
00:11:28,129 --> 00:11:29,249
mine.

208
00:11:36,690 --> 00:11:38,690
We haven't hugged like this for a long time.

209
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:45,389
Zhi Mei, are you okay?

210
00:11:47,009 --> 00:11:47,830
I'm fine.

211
00:11:49,409 --> 00:11:50,450
I'll go get something to drink.

212
00:12:19,389 --> 00:12:19,590
Zhi Mei.

213
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:20,590
It's me.

214
00:12:21,310 --> 00:12:22,470
I want to have a good talk with you.

215
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:23,970
Let's forget about the company.

216
00:12:24,369 --> 00:12:25,149
It's just you and me.

217
00:12:25,249 --> 00:12:25,749
Mr. Zhou,

218
00:12:26,629 --> 00:12:28,230
my wife went to change clothes.

219
00:12:29,310 --> 00:12:30,690
I can tell her what you want to say.

220
00:12:32,509 --> 00:12:33,749
Didn't Zhimei tell you that

221
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:36,249
your marriage registered overseas

222
00:12:36,789 --> 00:12:38,570
hasn't been notarized in China.

223
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:39,950
Legally,

224
00:12:40,509 --> 00:12:41,970
your marriage is not valid.

225
00:12:42,649 --> 00:12:43,009
She

226
00:12:43,409 --> 00:12:44,509
is not your wife.

227
00:12:45,009 --> 00:12:45,629
The law

228
00:12:46,710 --> 00:12:48,450
can't affect my relationship with Zhimei.

229
00:12:48,930 --> 00:12:50,749
It's none of your business.

230
00:12:51,529 --> 00:12:52,570
How do you know

231
00:12:53,529 --> 00:12:55,570
she still loves you?
